Help for VHOSTALL:

VHOSTALL allows operators to set a virtual host (also
known as a spoof or cloak) on all account nicks. This vhost
will be set on the user immediately and each time
they identify to their account. If no vhost is 
specified, clear all existing vhosts on account.

Syntax: VHOSTALL <nickname> [<vhost>]

Examples:
    /msg &nick& VHOSTALL spb may.explode.on.impact
    /msg &nick& VHOSTALL nenolod
